<sect1 id="dir_9d652bc49794ee57b22ecd7f52416e0b_1autotoc_md172">
<title>helios::engine::modules::pool</title><para>Object pool components for entity recycling.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_9d652bc49794ee57b22ecd7f52416e0b_1autotoc_md173">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides components related to object pooling, enabling efficient entity reuse without repeated allocation/deallocation.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_9d652bc49794ee57b22ecd7f52416e0b_1autotoc_md174">
